Hello. Well this map is a edit of the map named anticamper which many of you may know about as it is a popular map, and i noticed a few things that i didnt like about the map such as cornering and the textures and mainly just how plain the map is to play, So i decided to make a edit of anticamper and i hope you like it!

Anticamper_DanO_b1 is a well thought about map and i hope you like it!
If you have any questions or any ideas to change in the map let me know by commenting or you can email me at Oleary_95@hotmail.co.uk!

Modifications have been made to this map is so many ways such as NO MORE CORNERING, DIFFERENT TEXTURES, NEW THEME, NEW STYLE AND SOME OTHER LITTLE THINGS YOU WILL FIND AROUND THE MAP SUCH AS FISH AND A SHARK OUTSIDE THE MAP AND MUCH MORE!

I HOPE YOU LIKE MY MAP! PLEASE COMMENT AND VOTE MY MAP! THANK YOU!

If there is any other information you would like/need to know let me know and i will add more info ASAP!

THANK YOU!
